Kau seperti menyanderanya.

532
00:36:01,951 --> 00:36:03,536
Mari kita tanda tangan kontrak.

533
00:36:04,454 --> 00:36:05,997
Kenapa tiba-tiba bahas kontrak?

534
00:36:06,915 --> 00:36:09,751
