553
00:36:57,966 --> 00:36:59,092
Seon-gyeom adikku.

554
00:36:59,926 --> 00:37:02,470
Kekerasan terhadap sesama atlet…

555
00:37:03,138 --> 00:37:04,347
Kariernya bisa berakhir.

556
00:37:05,765 --> 00:37:09,310
Karena terlalu lama di Amerika,
