00:37:46,890 --> 00:37:47,891
Hukuman?

572
00:37:48,391 --> 00:37:49,559
Hukuman apa? Tak ada korban.

573
00:37:49,642 --> 00:37:51,728
Mereka bilang
ini bukan tindakan kekerasan,

574
